  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Mix together the chili flakes, mustard seeds, allspice, nutmeg, and ginger in a small bowl.",
    "Add the olive oil to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cannellini beans to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Spread the mixture out in a single layer on a baking sheet.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and stir in the lime juice.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
